Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是她的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界在消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後我也會漸漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我不想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 終於醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡迷糊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考試也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟悉的感觸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次睡眠過後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶都會漸漸變得模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真從容呢 考試考得不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次因為有長門幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少有點把握
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟經常去圖書館呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了好處你可要好好謝謝長門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得遊樂園不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼地方想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去遊樂園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在問長門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你們跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的這裏就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然還是覺得遊樂園好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像是第一次來舊書市場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每家店的種類都不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明明是文藝社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常好像跟書沒什麼緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺今天像是在社團活動一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長 暑段要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說文藝社暑假活動要怎麼安排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先想想安排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛有什麼點子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日祭嗎 這個不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,、是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是豐盛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是自己做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門也幫忙了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是幫忙上面衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼讓我品嚐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面衣也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟逛了不少地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 剛才的路還能再走兩倍遠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我會累垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起圖書館的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你還真可能去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門你剛才吃驚了一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 絕對沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你還真厲害啊阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟現在的長門相處得跟往常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食譜也買到了滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和文藝社的大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有把朝比奈學姐和鶴屋學姐也請過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想是這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得涼宮馬上就會覺得厭倦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是長門還是覺得兩個人比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人獨處 和阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 誤會什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡他的是之前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 身為Jk的朝倉 對這個好有興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是Jk呢 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實她的心情 能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是雖說理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在的我和以前的她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解的話 不已經算是戀愛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時一樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是毫無表情地偷看她和他的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單純的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感覺能摸到 卻又摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 不是我的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 我有了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 我將要從這個世界消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人在睡覺的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會進行身體的調整和記憶的整理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模糊的記憶變得清晰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有根據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但下次睡著睜開眼睛的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就會恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我將不再會是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何我堅信這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是星期日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所剩的重要的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好珍惜地度過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以長門來說還真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐想在外面吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 天氣很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什麼理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是上次去完古書市場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得喜歡外面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是特別的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你見識一下朝倉真正的手藝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣不告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是一氣做得太多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我相信長門一定會說好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算和她說了 結果也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會因此很傷心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能變回原來的我這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對她來說是值得高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算說出這種讓人不知所措的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對她來說也只是增添麻煩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面吃你做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比平時好吃很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超難為情 再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後我想笑著告別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後 我想看到朋友的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩遊戲時候的長門也會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一開始還以為是另外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近和之前的長門越來越像了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說記憶恢復的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一切不都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是因為和我和阿虛在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會變成這樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝自我意識過剩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 並不是單純的治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是恢復到從前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為有了他們 我才能成為真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去趟圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去做晚餐了待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於讀完這本書了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還了這本書之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是說有什麼遺憾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是沒能把自己的心意傳達給他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是什麼重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在圖書館借的書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多到了該還的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經看完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 剛看完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎是嗎 好像是SF吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個怎樣的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法直接說明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我換個問法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對長門老師來說那書精彩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頗有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頗有意思啊原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像在看三流戀愛小說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我看了簡介之後想看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣那我決定看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在這能跟你聊天的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門老師推薦的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓人失望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是別忘了還書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近老跟你去圖書館 去舊書市場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞的我都喜歡上讀書了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再去圖書館的話可以叫我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？長門？長門！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了？長門？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我還不了書了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我還嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 給我等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 你說這個是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有別岔開重要的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的告白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣的答覆都是未來的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪？你現在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說這種像以後不會再見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再見到我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會變回以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在那之前我一定要傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 還有一八請求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你到達的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個我醒的時候定會慌亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能送她到回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的感情傳達了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就沒有什麼好留戀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 似乎能觸碰的到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就該認知到這一天終會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的長門比以前的長門難聊上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才沒能發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼說也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生 我沒能注意到也是糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門你給我適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再見的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概會變回以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己要說的說完就擅自的消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 你是最棒的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧？這裏是哪裏啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚的公園裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我們兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這反應真讓人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 長門 好久不兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 欸？早安？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見？

